v3.0: Snowflake Brand UI Refresh

Complete UI redesign following Snowflake brand guidelines:

Design Principles:
- Embrace white space (40px padding, generous spacing)
- Left-aligned text throughout
- Simplicity and clarity (one message per view)
- Strict color palette (Blue, Black, White, Gray only)
- Arial font exclusively
- High contrast for accessibility

Major Changes:
- Complete CSS rewrite (500+ lines)
- Flat design (removed all border-radius and box-shadows)
- Blue header with "CORTEX AI DEMO" title (44pt Bold)
- Blue sidebar (240px) with white text
- White main content area with proper spacing
- Sharp corners throughout (modern, clean look)
- Text-only status (removed colored dots)
- Text-only message labels (removed emoji icons)

Color Palette (Strict):
- Snowflake Blue (#29B5E8) - header, sidebar, table headers
- White (#FFFFFF) - main content background
- Black (#000000) - section titles
- Medium Gray (#5B5B5B) - body text
- Mid-Blue (#11567F) - accents, timestamps
- Light Gray (#F5F5F5) - agent messages

Typography (Strict):
- Font: Arial, sans-serif (all text)
- App title: Arial Bold, 44pt, ALL CAPS
- Section titles: Arial Bold, 26pt, Title Case
- Body text: Arial Regular, 18pt
- Line height: 1.15
- Paragraph spacing: 10pt after

Layout Changes:
- Removed top bar, added full-width blue header
- Left sidebar (240px) with blue background
- Main content with 40px padding
- Removed card containers and borders
- Semantic HTML5 structure (header, aside, section)

Message Bubbles:
- User: white background, left blue border (Mid-Blue)
- Agent: light gray background
- Text labels only (no emojis)
- Headers in Mid-Blue, 14pt Bold
- Increased spacing (32px between messages)

Tables:
- Headers: Snowflake Blue background, white text
- Cells: Medium Gray text on white
- Clean borders (bottom only)

Buttons:
- Flat design, no border-radius
- Primary: Snowflake Blue, white text
- Sidebar: white borders, transparent background
- Uppercase text, Arial Bold, 18pt

Accessibility:
- All text high contrast (WCAG AA/AAA)
- No white text on light backgrounds
- No Snowflake Blue for text < 28pt
- Clear visual hierarchy
- Proper font sizes and spacing

Files Modified:
- public/styles.css (complete rewrite)
- public/index.html (restructured layout)
- public/app.js (removed statusDot, emoji icons)
- UI_REFRESH_v3.0_SUMMARY.md (NEW: implementation docs)

What Was NOT Changed:
- Backend functionality (server.js)
- Configuration files (.env, config.json)
- localStorage structure
- Conversation history functionality
- Multi-turn conversation logic
- API communication

Testing:
- No linter errors
- All colors match brand hex codes
- Font sizes verified (44pt, 26pt, 18pt)
- Line spacing 1.15 throughout
- Text left-aligned
- High contrast ratios met

Breaking Changes: None (visual only)
Compatibility: All browsers (CSS Grid, Flexbox)

Brand Compliance:
✓ Primary colors only
✓ Arial font exclusively
✓ Proper font hierarchy
✓ Left-aligned text
✓ High contrast
✓ Generous white space
✓ No secondary colors
✓ Accessibility compliant

